TneTabControl.SaveTabs(TExportElements,TSetOfStrings,TStringList) Method

Summary

Returns the number of the tabs

Saves the open tabs to a list of strings.

Namespace: neTabControl
Syntax
Delphi
public
 procedure SaveTabs(const exportElements: TExportElements;
 const excludeTabs: TSetOfStrings; var savedTabs: TStringList);

Parameters

exportElements
Type: TExportElements

Defines which elements will be used in the export data. See neTabTypes|TExportElements

excludeTabs
Type: TSetOfStrings

Defines which tabs (by tag) will be excluded from the save list

savedTabs
Type: TStringList

The list of saved tabs

Remarks

Export Structure

Tabs are exported as they appear in the tab.

  • [tag] = the tag of the neTabItem

  • [tagString] = the TagString property of the neTabItem

  • [tagFloat] = the TagFloat property of the neTabItem
